    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The Non-Lethal Flexible Ball Point Pens are a great option for providing a basic need in safe and responsible way for incarcerated inmates of jails, prisons, government detention centers, and mental health facilities. There is virtually no way to utilize these pens as a deadly weapon, they are essential writing tools for patients who may be prone to hurting themselves or others around them. These reliable flexible ball point pens are made with a soft bendable outer casing that does not harden, but melts when exposed to open flame; its rubbery material folds under pressure and is only 4.25 inches in length, making it nearly impossible to do lethal damage with. Ball point ink color is available in black or blue. Assembled in USA</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Federal Non-Lethal Flexible Ballpoint Pen Writing Instrument - BULK PENS</h2>\n  <p>The Non-Lethal Flexible Ball Point Pens are a great option for providing a basic need in safe and responsible way for incarcerated inmates of jails, prisons, government detention centers, and mental health facilities.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>INSTITUTIONAL SAFETY PEN:</strong> These non lethal bendable ink pens are an essential writing tool that allows for a basic need to be provided to people that may be prone to hurting themselves and others</li>\n    <li><strong>NON-LETHAL BENDABLE PEN:</strong> Designed to bend and flex under pressure while only being 4.25 inches in length, this flexible ball point pen maintains the highest safety standards</li>\n    <li><strong>INK FLOW WRITING CAPACITY:</strong> Each non-lethal jail pen contains a ink tube capable of writing up to 3500 feet before needing to be replaced or disposed</li>\n    <li><strong>JAIL PEN SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Length: 4.25&quot; | Weight: 0.001 oz. | Ink Color: Blue or Black</li>\n    <li>ASSEMBLED IN THE USA</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/PP_prison_pen_update_2_detail_09.jpg\" alt=\"The Non-Lethal Flexible Ball Point Pens are a great option for providing a basic need in safe and responsible way for incarcerated inmates of jails\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> PP1-BLU</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 766359589107</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>There is virtually no way to utilize these pens as a deadly weapon, they are essential writing tools for patients who may be prone to hurting themselves or others around them.</p>\n  <p>These reliable flexible ball point pens are made with a soft bendable outer casing that does not harden, but melts when exposed to open flame; its rubbery material folds under pressure and is only 4.25 inches in length, making it nearly impossible to do lethal damage with.</p>\n  <p>Ball point ink color is available in black or blue. Assembled in USA</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
